readable.content: A bride and groom look at each other in a goofy picture . A bridge is talking to the groom and he scratches his head . A formally dressed couple , she with her mouth open , stand next to each other . A groom and a bride with a strapless dress . A man in a black suit knocks his head with his fist as he puts his arm around a woman in a white strapless dress .
